correct_usage_1("javax.crypto.Cipher.init", label_init, var_init, in_meth) :- 
    call("javax.crypto.Cipher.init", label_init, var_init, in_meth), 
    init_with_correct_mode(var_init, label_init, in_meth),
    exception_handling(label_init, in_meth).

init_with_correct_mode(var_init, label_init, in_meth) :-
    actual_argument("javax.crypto.Cipher.init", arg_mode, label_init, 1, in_meth), 
    mode_condition(arg_mode, label_init, in_meth).

mode_condition(arg_mode, label_init, in_meth):- 
    value(arg_mode, label_value, in_meth),
    (label_value = "Cipher.ENCRYPT_MODE"; 
    label_value = "Cipher.DECRYPT_MODE"; 
    label_value = "Cipher.WRAP_MODE"; 
    label_value = "Cipher.UNWRAP_MODE").

exception_handling(label_init, in_meth) :-
    flow_reach(label_try, in_meth, label_init, in_meth),
    catch("java.security.InvalidKeyException", _, label_catch, _, _, in_meth),
    flow_reach(label_init, in_meth, label_catch, in_meth).
